OL,3,CMPs concerned that risk of
OL,4,Chomelessness among Ukrainians in UK
OL,5,Clikely to rise
OL,7,FThe risk of homelessness among
OL,8,FUkrainians who fled to the UK to
OL,9,Fescape the war is likely to increase
OL,10,Fas more sponsorships end or break
OL,11,Fdown, MPs have warned.
OL,13,FA new report from the Public Accounts
OL,14,FCommittee said it had asked the
OL,15,FGovernment why it did not have a "full
OL,16,Fand accurate picture" of homelessness
OL,17,Famong people on the Homes for Ukraine
OL,18,Fscheme.
OL,26,@wD@bOUxD@UO]
