OL,3,CMPs concerned that risk of
OL,4,Chomelessness among Ukrainians in UK
OL,5,Clikely to rise
OL,7,FIt noted that 30% of English local
OL,8,Fauthorities "regularly failed to
OL,9,Fprovide homelessness data" for those
OL,10,Fon the scheme.
OL,12,FIts report said the Department for
OL,13,FLevelling Up, Housing and Communities
OL,14,F(DLUHC) explained that the data it
OL,15,Freceived from more than 70% of local
OL,16,Fauthorities was "representative and
OL,17,Fsufficient to track trends so that it
OL,18,Fcould respond accordingly with policy
OL,19,Finterventions".
OL,26,@pD@MOUqD@ZO]xD@QOU{D@NO]
