OL,3,CMPs concerned that risk of
OL,4,Chomelessness among Ukrainians in UK
OL,5,Clikely to rise
OL,7,FBut the committee said: "We are
OL,8,Fconcerned that the risk of
OL,9,Fhomelessness among Ukrainians in the
OL,10,FUK is likely to increase as more
OL,11,Fsponsorships end or break down."
OL,13,FThe MPs said that by the end of August
OL,14,Flast year, local authorities had
OL,15,Freported that 4,890 Ukrainian
OL,16,Fhouseholds in England who were in the
OL,17,FUK on Homes for Ukraine visas had been
OL,18,Fhomeless or come within 56 days of
OL,19,Fbeing homeless.
OL,26,@oD@YOUsD@`O]
