OL,3,CMPs concerned that risk of
OL,4,Chomelessness among Ukrainians in UK
OL,5,Clikely to rise
OL,7,FThe report added that, since the
OL,8,Fbeginning of 2023, "at any one time,
OL,9,Fbetween 600 and 800 Ukrainian
OL,10,Fhouseholds have been living in
OL,11,Ftemporary accommodation in England,
OL,12,Falthough DLUHC does not know how many
OL,13,Fof these households are part of the
OL,14,FHomes for Ukraine scheme".
OL,26,@pD@TOUvD@YO]
