OL,3,CMPs concerned that risk of
OL,4,Chomelessness among Ukrainians in UK
OL,5,Clikely to rise
OL,7,FThe MPs recommended the department
OL,8,Fshould increase the number of local
OL,9,Fauthorities that regularly provide
OL,10,Fhomelessness data and secure an
OL,11,Fadequate supply of sponsors for the
OL,12,Fscheme in the future in a cost-
OL,13,Feffective way.
OL,15,FThe report also said a slowdown in
OL,16,Fprocessing visas "is leaving some
OL,17,FUkrainians facing an unacceptably long
OL,18,Fwait for decisions to be made on their
OL,19,Fapplications".
OL,26,@xD@ROU{D@MO]
