OL,3,CMPs concerned that risk of
OL,4,Chomelessness among Ukrainians in UK
OL,5,Clikely to rise
OL,7,FIt said that despite changes brought
OL,8,Fin by the Home Office, "visa
OL,9,Fturnaround times have taken longer
OL,10,Fsince June 2022" with 63% of visa
OL,11,Fapplications taking more than the 15
OL,12,Fworking day target to be processed in
OL,13,FJuly 2023, compared to 19% in June
OL,14,F2022.
OL,16,FMPs urged the department to set out
OL,17,Fits plan for if there is a future
OL,18,Fsurge in applications, and to publish
OL,19,Fquarterly updates on visa processing
OL,20,Ftimes for the remainder of the scheme.
OL,26,@pD@XOUrD@PO]
