OL,3,CMPs concerned that risk of
OL,4,Chomelessness among Ukrainians in UK
OL,5,Clikely to rise
OL,7,FThe report was put together before the
OL,8,FGovernment's recent announcement of an
OL,9,F18-month visa extension scheme,
OL,10,Fsomething committee chair Dame Meg
OL,11,FHillier welcomed.
OL,13,FHowever, concerns have been raised
OL,14,Fover the Home Office's closure of the
OL,15,FUkraine family scheme which happened
OL,16,Fon Monday afternoon.
OL,18,FThe Ukraine family scheme allowed
OL,19,Fapplicants to join family members or
OL,20,Fextend their stay in the UK.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/15
