OL,3,CMPs concerned that risk of
OL,4,Chomelessness among Ukrainians in UK
OL,5,Clikely to rise
OL,7,FAn extension scheme, which meant
OL,8,FUkrainian nationals and their
OL,9,Fimmediate relatives could apply for
OL,10,Fpermission to remain in the country,
OL,11,Fis due to close on May 16.
OL,13,FDame Meg said: "We look forward to
OL,14,Fhearing how much more certainty it
OL,15,F(the Government) is able provide to
OL,16,Fthose staying in the UK, particularly
OL,17,Fin light of the recent closure of the
OL,18,FUkraine Family Scheme.
OL,26,@uD@POU
