OL,3,CMPs concerned that risk of
OL,4,Chomelessness among Ukrainians in UK
OL,5,Clikely to rise
OL,7,F"As the war has continued the
OL,8,Fchallenge now is that thousands of
OL,9,FUkrainian households were homeless or
OL,10,Fclose to it last year.
OL,12,F"Not only is this a huge problem but
OL,13,Four report finds that there is no full
OL,14,Foversight of homelessness within the
OL,15,Fscheme itself.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU
