OL,3,CMPs concerned that risk of
OL,4,Chomelessness among Ukrainians in UK
OL,5,Clikely to rise
OL,7,F"There are of course factors here
OL,8,Fwhich make long-term planning
OL,9,Fchallenging, not least the continuing
OL,10,Funcertainty in Ukraine itself. But the
OL,11,FGovernment must ensure it has a plan
OL,12,Fto support those who have sought
OL,13,Fsafety in the UK."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@RO]
