OL,4,Chomelessness among Ukrainians in UK
OL,5,Clikely to rise
OL,7,FThe report said while the Homes for
OL,8,FUkraine scheme had been set up at
OL,9,Fspeed and helped tens of thousands of
OL,10,FUkrainians come to the UK, the
OL,11,Fdepartment "does not know fully what
OL,12,Faspects of the scheme have or have not
OL,13,Fworked and whether overall the scheme
OL,14,Fhas been value for money".
OL,26,@sD@LOUvD@YO]
