OL,3,CMPs concerned that risk of
OL,4,Chomelessness among Ukrainians in UK
OL,5,Clikely to rise
OL,7,FThe MPs said the department should set
OL,8,Fout its plans to evaluate the scheme,
OL,9,Fincluding how lessons learned and best
OL,10,Fpractice examples could be used for
OL,11,Fpotential future resettlement schemes,
OL,12,Fand a consideration of the overall
OL,13,Fvalue for money of the scheme.
OL,15,FThe committee also urged the
OL,16,FGovernment to set out its assessment
OL,17,Fof its commercial options once the
OL,18,Fcurrent contract, held by tech giant
OL,19,FPalantir, expires.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G12/15
