OL,3,CMPs concerned that risk of
OL,4,Chomelessness among Ukrainians in UK
OL,5,Clikely to rise
OL,7,FIt said: "If this includes extending
OL,8,Fthe contract with Palantir, DLUHC
OL,9,Fshould explain how this is justified
OL,10,Funder current procurement regulations.
OL,12,F"In particular, how such a decision
OL,13,Fwould be consistent with the
OL,14,FGovernment Chief Commercial Officer's
OL,15,Fconcerns about departments accepting
OL,16,FIT companies' offers to provide free
OL,17,Ftrial periods to gain a commercial
OL,18,Ffoothold."
