OL,7,FThe latest figures showed that there
OL,8,Fhad been 200,600 arrivals of Ukraine
OL,9,FScheme visa-holders in the UK as of
OL,10,FFebruary 19.
OL,12,FThere had been 56,900 arrivals through
OL,13,Fthe Ukraine Family Scheme and 143,700
OL,14,Fthrough the Homes for Ukraine scheme
OL,15,F(also know as the Ukraine Sponsorship
OL,16,FScheme).
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G14/15
