OL,3,CMPs concerned that risk of
OL,4,Chomelessness among Ukrainians in UK
OL,5,Clikely to rise
OL,7,FRoger Gough, from the Local Government
OL,8,FAssociation, said housing shortages
OL,9,F"compounded by the pressures of
OL,10,Fmultiple asylum and resettlement
OL,11,Fschemes" have resulted in "a high
OL,12,Fnumber of Ukrainians having to turn to
OL,13,Fcouncils for housing and homelessness
OL,14,Fsupport".
OL,16,FHe called for an "urgent review" of
OL,17,Fthe funding arrangements for councils
OL,18,Fas well as existing and new hosts
OL,19,Fwhich he said "were designed to fund
OL,20,Ftemporary sanctuary".
